data.description: This charming home is situated on a spacious 0.83-acre lot, offering plenty of room for outdoor activities and potential expansion. The open floor plan creates a seamless flow between the living room, kitchen, and dining area, perfect for modern living and entertaining guests. As you enter the home, you're greeted by a welcoming living room featuring large windows that fill the space with natural light and offer views of the beautiful surrounding landscape. The kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting ample cabinet space, high-quality appliances, and a convenient island for meal preparation and casual dining.
